Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
My favorite movie is Harry Potter, which is an esential part of my teenage life. It describes the life experience of a boy with magical power but living in a normal world. Afrer he got to know the world which he belongs to, he had to struggle with the devil. In the process, he learns to confront fear and sorrow and balance his needs and  the public expectations.